data.text:
Heading to the 2024 Nhill Airshow? Secure your seat aboard the historic DC3 ‘Gooney Bird’. Departing Essendon Fields Airport, this will be an unforgettable experience. With seats limited, now is the time to book to arrive in grand style.

Free entry to the Airshow included in the fare.

JANUARY SPECIAL: $30 discount
